---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import CtaBand from '../components/CtaBand.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Trucker Copilot Features | Documents, Funding and Signals"
  description="Explore Trucker Copilot features for mobile document capture, load submission, funding status, communication, broker information, and carrier operations."
>
  <section class="hero" style="padding-bottom:2.5rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Features</span>
      <h1>Less chasing. More control.</h1>
      <p class="lead" style="color:var(--text-muted); max-width:44em;">
        Trucker Copilot brings the load, the evidence, the conversation, and the financial status
        together. Drivers stay focused on the road. Carriers gain control over what happens after
        delivery.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="padding-top:1rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Load and document workflow</h2>
      <div class="grid grid--2 mt-2 mb-2">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon">📸</div>
          <h3>Mobile document capture</h3>
          <p>Photograph and upload invoices, rate confirmations, bills of lading, proof of delivery, receipts, and supporting documents from your phone.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon">🤖</div>
          <h3>AI document reading</h3>
          <p>Convert uploaded paperwork into organized transaction data that can move through review without repetitive typing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon">📦</div>
          <h3>Delivery confirmation</h3>
          <p>Record delivery activity and connect the event to the documents that support the completed load.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon">📤</div>
          <h3>Completed load submission</h3>
          <p>Send the full transaction to your participating finance company from the app.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>Funding and financial visibility</h2>
      <div class="grid grid--2 mt-2 mb-2">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon">💰</div>
          <h3>Funding status</h3>
          <p>See where submitted transactions stand without calling for an update.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon">👥</div>
          <h3>Shared transaction visibility</h3>
          <p>Keep authorized drivers, dispatchers, fleet staff, and finance teams connected to the same record.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon">🔍</div>
          <h3>Broker and shipper information</h3>
          <p>Review available credit and operating information before accepting risk, subject to provider access and connected data services.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon">🤝</div>
          <h3>Finance company connection</h3>
          <p>Request access to participating specialty finance companies that understand transportation receivables.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>Communication and access</h2>
      <div class="grid grid--2 mt-2 mb-2">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon">💬</div>
          <h3>Contextual communication</h3>
          <p>Keep questions, requests, and answers attached to the load instead of scattered across calls and text messages.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon">🌎</div>
          <h3>Multilingual interaction</h3>
          <p>Support clearer communication across drivers, dispatchers, and operating teams.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon">📶</div>
          <h3>Variable connectivity support</h3>
          <p>Work through the changing network conditions drivers face on the road.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card__icon">🔐</div>
          <h3>Role based access</h3>
          <p>Give drivers, dispatchers, carrier managers, and authorized partners access appropriate to their responsibilities.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>On the road with Trucker Copilot</h2>
      <div class="grid grid--3 mt-2 mb-2" style="justify-items:center;">
        <div class="phone-frame"><img src="/img/app/route-map.jpg" alt="Route map with fuel prices along the route" loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="phone-frame"><img src="/img/app/matching-loads.jpg" alt="Matching loads list with origin and destination" loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="phone-frame"><img src="/img/app/fuel-stop.jpg" alt="Fuel stop detail with discounted diesel price" loading="lazy" /></div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero__grid mb-2" style="align-items:center;">
        <div>
          <h2>Fuel savings with the LoadConnex fuel card</h2>
          <p style="color:var(--text-muted); font-size:1.1rem;">
            Cut one of your biggest costs at the pump. The LoadConnex fuel card connects to Trucker
            Copilot so you can find participating stops along your route, compare retail and
            discounted prices before you commit, and keep fuel activity part of your operating
            record.
          </p>
          <p style="color:var(--text-faint); font-size:0.92rem;">
            Discounts vary by location, network, and program terms.
          </p>
        </div>
        <img src="/img/photos/loadconnex-card.png" alt="LoadConnex fuel card" loading="lazy" style="filter: drop-shadow(0 16px 32px rgba(13,25,62,0.25));" />
      </div>

      <h2>Connected ecosystem <span class="badge-soon">Expanding</span></h2>
      <div class="section__intro">
        <p>
          Trucker Copilot is designed to connect with transportation and financial systems through
          FactorEvo, including FMCSA data, credit information, load and transportation systems,
          accounting, banking, ELD and telematics, load boards, and fuel networks where enabled.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaBand
    headline="Put the whole transaction in one place."
    primaryLabel="Get Trucker Copilot"
    primaryHref="/download"
    secondaryLabel="Talk With Our Team"
    secondaryHref="/about"
  />
</Base>
